  • Rahul Mishra Jha ji maine keval aapke 2000 rupaye cash donation limit par rakhe gaye mat ka khandan kiya hai.. jaha tak Hindu dharmik sansthao ka prashn hai.. ve kaafi samay se law ke antargat nigrani me rakhi gayi hai jabki Muslim evam Christian organizations ko autonomous sansthao me rakha gaya Kuch naam Bhar ki committee commission ityadi ke antargat.. to Hindu sansthao par achanak se koi nayi nigrani aarambh nahi ho gayi hai.. shayad aapka vichaar yah hai ki Hindu sanshaye ab tak kaala paisa jama karke chal rahi thi Jo daandaatao ke naam records me aane se baith jaayengi... Aapki 2000 rupaye ki limit ki aalochana, mere prati vyangaatmak shaili aur yah vyarth ka krodh MERI samajh se pare hai.. koi truti ho to fir se kshamaprarthy hu..

    Vijay Malya ko Maine maatra udaharan ke taur par rakha.. defaulters ki vajah se banks ko achcha khaasa nuksaan uthana padta hai atah Maine isko neechi byaaj daro ke kaaran me se ek rakha.. byaaj ka antar hi banks ka munafa hota hai jisse vah chalta hai.. jaane mere comment me aapne kaha padh liya ki Vijay Malya Bharatiya poonjiwaad ka pratinidhitwa karte hai.. jaha tak poonjipatiyo ke aadhipatya ki baat hai.. aap maane ya na maane Unka bahut bhaari prabhav sabhi rajnaitic dalo par rahta hai.. Jo ki governments bhi chalate hai.. tax Daan par nahi aay par lagta hai.. dharmik sansthao ko Daan dene par kisi Badi chhoot ka koi pravdhan kabhi nahi raha hai.. sansthao k haath me yah karmukt hota hai uske liye bhi alag niyam hai.. yadyapi main jaanta hu ki aapko iska gyaan hai kintu fir bhi aapko trusts se sambandhit Aaykar niyamo ko aur jaanne ki aawashyakta hai.. chooki yah mera kaaryakshetra hi hai to mujhe laga ki tippani kar du.. galti ho gayi lagta hai.. fir se kshama chaahunga.. raajnaitik dalo ke baare me bhi sun Lein.. yaha par aapka Raajnaitik dalo ka ullekh karna ut pataang hai kyoki Dharmik sansthao ka uddeshya seva hai jabki Raajnaitik dalo ka note chhaapna... Raajnaitik dalo ka RTI me aana anivaarya hai saaf raajneeti ke liye isse aap bhi sahmat hai... Fir bhi charcha ke vishay se door nahi jaana chaahunga.. 2000 limit par aapki raay se main sahmat nahi hu.. mere vichaar se yah ek badaa hi achcha nirnay hai.. aasha hai yadi aapne aage uttar dena uchit samjha to katu vyangaatmak bhasha ka prayog nahi karenge..
